		<p><strong>优惠</strong>：<br />1. 半价丰胸体验，原价$128，现价$64，每人只限一次<br />2. 中医美容项目，两人同行一人免单，可从下面的Group 1 or Group 2中任选两个同样价位的面部保养项目，每人只限一次</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p> </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>介绍</strong>：<br />C.O.R.E.亚健康调理中心，我们利用传统中医和现代科技结合进行：乳腺保养、物理丰胸、纤体瘦身、中医美容、灸疗养生、回阳祛湿，淋巴排毒、疏通经络，调理脏腑，调和阴阳使气血平衡。我们将以专业的产品、精密的仪器，专业的技能，独特的项目、贴心优质的服务为您带来健康、美丽、优雅、自信。</p>
<p>中医美容优惠<br />两人同行一人免单，中医美容，可从下面的Group 1 or Group 2中任选两个同样价位的面部保养项目，每人只限一次<br />Group 1:<br />Whitening Facial&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;90mins/ $80<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入维他命C精华，补水面膜+<br />美白护理面膜。使皮肤美白，有光泽。<br />Clean, exfoliation face，neck，shoulder and breast lymphatic detox massage using ultrasonic machine with vitamin C serum, soothing gel mask + treatment mask, this facial is whiten and brighten up the face.<br />Sensitive Facial &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..90mins/ $80<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入抗敏感啫喱，补水面膜 + 抗敏感<br />护理面膜。 使敏感皮肤消红肿，恢复健康。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic machine with sensitive gel to achieve a balanced and calm complexion, soothing gel mask +treatment mask.<br />Acne Facial&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.90mins/ $80<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下 淋巴按摩，超声仪导入PH平衡啫喱精华，补水<br />面膜+ 祛痘护理面膜。减少皮肤多余油脂，平衡皮肤水分，使肌肤恢复健康。<br />Clean, super extractor lotion, extractions, face, neck, shoulder and breast lymphatic detox<br />massage, using ultrasonic machine with hydro PH balance gel, soothing gel mask + treatment<br />mask, this facial is a purifying, decongesting and healing face.<br />Hydration Facial&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..90mins/ $80<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下 淋巴按摩，超声仪导入补水啫喱，补水面膜 + 护理面膜。<br />使肌肤水润饱满。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic machine with hydro gel, soothing gel mask+ treatment mask, this is a relaxing and refreshing facial.<br />Group 2:<br />Hydration Ampule Treatment&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;90mins/ $109<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入高补水安瓿，补水面膜 + 护理 面膜。<br />使缺水的肌肤恢复水嫩光滑，紧实饱满。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic machine with soothing ampule, soothing gel mask+ treatment mask. Firming and refreshing face.</p>
<p>Collagen Treatment&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..90mins/ $109<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入骨胶原修复精华，补水面膜+骨胶原<br />护理面膜。及时补充肌肤流失的胶原蛋白，提升肌肤紧实度，深层滋养，由内至外改善肌肤丰润度。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and Breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic machine with collagen serum, soothing gel mask + collagen treatment mask, this treatment moisturize the skin, helpingdiminish wrinkles&amp; softening the face</p>
<p>Placenta Treatment&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;90mins/ $109<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入胎盘素修复精华，补水面膜+深层<br />护理面膜。改善皮肤弹性，减少细纹，均衡水分及油脂，促进细胞再生，增加皮肤滋润度。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and Breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic machine with placenta serum, soothing gel mask + treatment mask, this treatment is improve elasticity, help cell regeneration, reduce wrinkles, moisturize the skin.</p>
<p>Oxygen Treatment&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;..90mins/ $109<br />清洁，去角质，面部、颈部、肩部、胸部及腋下淋巴按摩，超声仪导入Oxygen修复精华，补水面膜+ oxygen<br />护理面膜。改善色素沉淀，帮助皮肤新陈代谢，使肌肤美白滋润健康。<br />Clean, exfoliation, face, neck, shoulder and breast lymphatic detox massage, using ultrasonic<br />machine with oxygen serum, soothing gel mask oxygen treatment mask, this treatment inhibits<br />melanin and whitens the skin.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
